Embedded fonts — licensing
===========================

All three fonts embedded into text_shaper.wasm are licensed under the
Apache License, Version 2.0 (http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0):

- Roboto-Regular.ttf       — Roboto, © Google (Christian Robertson)
- RobotoSlab-Regular.ttf   — Roboto Slab, © The Roboto Slab Project Authors
- RobotoMono-Regular.ttf   — Roboto Mono, © The Roboto Mono Project Authors

The Apache-2.0 license permits embedding and redistribution (including
inside a compiled WebAssembly binary) provided the license and
attribution are retained — which this file does.

Sources:
- https://github.com/googlefonts/roboto
- https://github.com/googlefonts/robotoslab
- https://github.com/googlefonts/RobotoMono
